===Ascension===
Heroes have ascension tiers. {{A-Level}} heroes start at Elite tier and {{S-Level}} heroes start at Epic tier and be ascended to higher tiers using their respective [[Soul Sigil]]s or [[Acorn]]s at specific tiers. {{Hero|Chippy|nobr=1}} and {{Hero|Hammie|nobr=1}} are Rare tier heroes that cannot be ascended.

